+# Exploration 001 Summary - Raw Exact Closure Ledger For `F_SS(1/12)`
+
+- Goal:
+  reconstruct the raw exact closure burden of the frozen witness
+  `F_SS(1/12)` and separate pre-frozen witness content from genuinely
+  closure-forced additions.
+- What I tried:
+  read the Step-7 witness freeze,
+  the Step-4 `F_SS` dossier,
