+
+- Goal:
+  reconstruct the raw exact closure burden of the frozen witness `F_SS(1/12)`
+  on the Step-7 canonical one-bridge ledger, separating already frozen content,
+  mandatory conjugate completion, closure-forced same-scale / feedback /
+  cross-scale burden, and the point where the local record stops supporting a
+  finite exact mode list.
