+- `missions/exact-ns-no-near-closed-tao-circuit/planning-runs/run-002/attacks/chain-03.md`
+- `missions/exact-ns-no-near-closed-tao-circuit/planning-runs/run-002/attacks/chain-01.md`
+- `missions/exact-ns-no-near-closed-tao-circuit/controller/decisions/decision-011.md`
+
+## Deliverable
+
+Write:
+
+- `REPORT.md` with the class-retention / finiteness verdict, no-rescue audit,
+  and Step-3-readiness decision.
+- `REPORT-SUMMARY.md` with a concise verdict suitable for the step history.
+
+## Constraints
+
+- Remain inside the Step-7 same-currency rule.
+- Do not reopen broad mission planning.
+- Do not run dynamics or compare dynamic outputs to `G_tmpl` / `G_leak`.
+- If the local record only supports a non-isolability memo, state that plainly
+  and stop there.
